                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        Minister <persName type="to">Rockhill</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1905-07-24">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 24, 1905</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Adee authorizes Mr. Rockhill to sound other legations in regard to the
                    protection of trade-marks in China, and, if they be duly authorized by their
                    governments, to effect arrangements by an exchange of notes on the basis of the
                    British precedent.)</p>
            </div>
